high_descs: Turn to face the counter next to the refrigerator, walk towards it.
Take the white mug out of the upper cabinet next to the fridge.
Put the white mug in the microwave on the plate and heat it up, remove it again.
Turn left and then walk to the end of the room, turn right at the door and face the black table.
Set the white mug down on the table in the lower right-hand corner.
anns.task_desc: Heat up a white mug to set it down on the black table.

high_descs: Turn to your right and go to the cabinet above the small counter top between the refrigerator and the stove.
Pull out the white coffee mug inside the cabinet.
Move over to your right so that you are in front of the microwave above the stove.
Place the cup in the microwave, heat it up, then remove the coffee cup from the microwave.
Turn around and walk across the room, turn right at the door and go to the small, black shelf in the corner of the room across from you.
Place the coffee cup on the front, right corner of the small, black shelf.
anns.task_desc: Put a warm coffee cup on the black shelf.

high_descs: move forwards to the right side of the fridge up ahead on the left
grab a cup out of the cabinet to the top right of the fridge
move to the right a bit and face the microwave on the left above the stove
place the cup inside the microwave, turn it on, then take it back out once it is done
turn around and walk over to the opposite side of the room where the black table is in the right side corner of the room
place the cup down on the black table there in the corner of the room
anns.task_desc: place a microwaved cup down on the black table in the corner of the room
